Lynxiz is suprised when Trinity smashes into her hind section. 
"Whoa," Her natural instincts kick in and she immediately tries to 
pin Tirinity to the ground. As soon as she sees the little bot, she 
draws her paw away. "Why, why hello little one, what are you 
doing here?!" She turns to face Trinity and sits down, eye level 
about a metre away from the little bot.
